signatures.text: fun CharSequence.indexOfAny( chars: CharArray, startIndex: Int = 0, ignoreCase: Boolean = false): Int
signatures.desc: Finds the index of the first occurrence of any of the specified chars in this char sequence, starting from the specified startIndex and optionally ignoring the case.

signatures.text: fun CharSequence.indexOfAny( strings: Collection<String>, startIndex: Int = 0, ignoreCase: Boolean = false): Int
signatures.desc: Finds the index of the first occurrence of any of the specified strings in this char sequence, starting from the specified startIndex and optionally ignoring the case.
